body:
You cannot use this form to complain about:

* the result of a case
* a judge, magistrate, coroner or member of a tribunal
body:cy:
WELSH: You cannot use this form to complain about:

* the result of a case
* a judge, magistrate, coroner or member of a tribunal
heading: Complain about a court or tribunal service
heading:cy: WELSH: Gwneud cwyn am un o wasanaethau'r llysoedd neu'r tribiwnlysoedd
lede: Your complaint will not affect your case.
lede:cy: WELSH: Your complaint will not affect your case.
